  "texts": [
    "In 2020, the UK's decision to use an algorithm to predict A-level grades led to a public outcry.",
    "The algorithm disproportionately downgraded students from disadvantaged backgrounds while favoring those from affluent schools.",
    "This is just one out of many cases of how algorithms perpetuate existing biases.",
    "For instance, an 1 3",
    "International Journal of Artificial Intelligence in Education (2024 Education 34:1510 Education (-1540 algorithm developed to identify at-risk students performed worse for African-American students (Hu & Rangwala, 2020)."
  ]
}